Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:43.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any sense...\Nof being in school right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.04,0:01:49.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And I can't feel the fact that I was beaten\Nby those guys from Soul Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:50.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,almost killed by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:56.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or the fact that she's\Nnot here right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:02:03.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or the fact that not one of\Nmy classmates remembers Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.66,0:02:06.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bohahaha...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:08.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are you still into that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:12.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what? The time's ripe for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.52,0:02:15.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime, have you made plans\Nfor summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:17.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.23,0:02:20.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime, then come and\Nstay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My parents will be going abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:25.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:27.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know exactly what you're up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:28.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Is this what it means...\N– I'm not even thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:30.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– to go back to the Soul Society?\N– about bathing together or anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.52,0:02:31.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you blabbering about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:36.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You disappear from this world\Nand from people's memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:41.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Every evidence of her existence\Ndisappears...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:44.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,into white.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.63,0:02:52.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...\NThat's about it for reminders.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:56.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, students,\Ndon't die before September!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:57.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Class dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.80,0:02:58.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.88,0:03:08.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That Ishida cut class, after all.\NI thought he might still remember Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:09.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.43,0:03:13.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Turn! Turn! Turn! Turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, where's the watermelon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:20.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.55,0:03:22.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That’s right!\NSummer means the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And the sea means summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:25.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I, Keigo Asano,\Nam planning
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.69,0:03:30.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,a 10-day trip to the seaside\Nfrom tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:33.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks, scary outings,\Nand even a co-ed outdoors bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.87,0:03:37.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lots and lots of things to do,\Nboth fun and embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I have plans, so I’ll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, too.\NI'm not too keen on the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:45.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've got an inter-high tournament,\Nso I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:50.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If Orihime and Tatsuki aren't going,\Nthen I guess I won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.57,0:03:53.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go this time, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:58.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry,\NI'm leaving for Hawaii tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:04:02.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! With that older girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.04,0:04:06.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, with her and\Nher nine other friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.24,0:04:08.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so that makes 11 of us\Nincluding myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.28,0:04:09.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's you\Nand ten other girls?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he always pick on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strange...nothing feels out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:31.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even with Rukia gone,\Nour world continues to turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:37.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... Rukia was originally\Nfrom the other world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:41.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There was really no place\Nfor her here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:45.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then what'll I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:50.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:55.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NSomething wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:57.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Rukia go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:03.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why has everyone suddenly\Nforgotten about Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would know, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:14.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then Rukia returned to\Nthe world she came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:16.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:22.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But what a shock.\NThat you were able to see through us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:24.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since when?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:27.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the incident\Nwith my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.66,0:05:28.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:31.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:32.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.52,0:05:36.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really grateful about that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:38.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You guided my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:44.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's happy\Non the other side. I can feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:45.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.34,0:05:46.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:50.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Rukia is doing well\Non the other side, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She probably has family\Nand friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:05:59.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have to bring her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:03.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...if she's happy there...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:08.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's in a predicament where\Nshe could be killed any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:16.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, you'll probably say this:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:20.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if she has family\Nor friends over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.70,0:06:22.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she's alive,\Nthey'll be able to meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If she's dead, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:30.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You already know what\Nyou want to do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.88,0:06:41.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She was really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.31,0:06:44.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And her place is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.72,0:07:00.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:14.06,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.88,0:07:20.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How boring! It's summer vacation\Nand Ichigo goes off without us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.25,0:07:22.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu, it’s about time you--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:26.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! How about sleeping\Nin Dad's bed tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.72,0:07:32.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your jokes!\NAnd just talk in your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.62,0:07:34.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, just thinking about that\Nmakes me feel uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:38.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gee...those words really hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Lieutenant Abarai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:56.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin’!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:04.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:07.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you fly away,\NI'll get in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:16.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! I'm Jennifer. I'm a blood type A,\NPisces. E-cup bra size and--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.80,0:08:19.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.26,0:08:23.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji! Aren't you off duty today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.72,0:08:28.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to check on the prisoner.\NIs she still sulking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.30,0:08:31.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not sulking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:34.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:37.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just not hungry,\N“Mr. Lieutenant.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.58,0:08:42.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You got a problem that\NI'm the Lieutenant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.01,0:08:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.97,0:08:46.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Way to go, Mr. Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:48.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are so strong, Mr. Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyebrows look so weird,\NMr. Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:54.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--! I'll kill you!\NCome out of there, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Say Renji...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:56.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.96,0:09:01.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.46,0:09:05.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! It'll be immediate execution\Nfor someone like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:07.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:11.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:16.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! I was just joking.\NJust a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:17.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it, idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:22.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the idiot here?\NMaking us worry with your antics.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:27.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki is probably asking\Nfor clemency right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:31.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:37.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fool! He's your older brother!\NAs if he'd let his sister die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He would kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.31,0:09:44.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know full well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:50.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of man he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.26,0:09:54.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Forty years after being taken in\Nby the Kuchiki family...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he has never once looked at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.50,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA STORE\NCLOSED TODAY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.92,0:10:20.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:25.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine! A huge cavern\Nbeneath the shop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.86,0:10:32.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pipe down! You don't have to yell.\NI'm pretty damn surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:34.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:38.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get started with this\N"lesson" or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:41.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right, as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:50.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.80,0:10:57.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to breathe, huh?\NWhen you're in the form of a soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:11:01.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, your Soul Sleep, which is\Nthe wellspring of your spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:04.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and the Soul Chain, the booster,\Nhave been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:06.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:09.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,your soul is like that of the average person\Nwho has no spiritual power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.38,0:11:15.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So first, we must restore\Nthe spiritual power you have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then what do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:21.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, rather than explain it,\Nwhy don't we just do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:24.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:33.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.32,0:11:37.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson one! Please fight her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:38.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.92,0:11:40.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:44.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson One will be over once\Neither one of you are rendered immobile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:46.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please knock her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:50.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding?! You expect me\Nto hit a little girl like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:53.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be quite difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.18,0:11:57.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please put those on properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:11:59.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.07,0:12:04.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is so silly! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See? Don't say I didn't warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:19.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:21.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.17,0:12:29.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's going after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.34,0:12:32.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, he ran right past her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:37.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes! What was that?!\NIf I get hit with that, I’m dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.98,0:12:40.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! How do I put this on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.77,0:12:42.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, your forehead!\NYour forehead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.92,0:12:44.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.02,0:12:47.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And then, you holler\Nas loud as you can:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:49.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Power of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Armor of justice!\NJustice headband! In place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:57.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Awright!\NAs if I can do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.57,0:13:02.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See? No time to feel embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:06.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! Power of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:09.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Armor of justice!\NJustice headband! In place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.59,0:13:13.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, he actually did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:15.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you! Behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:19.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aw man...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Awright, come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.09,0:13:29.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! This thing isn't any good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:32.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I run around like this,\NI'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:33.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.72,0:13:36.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I can run around,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.41,0:13:38.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,it means I'm keeping up\Nwith her speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.57,0:13:40.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:43.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:48.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:50.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:56.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't aim for her face.\NJust a little blow to her headgear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.39,0:13:59.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, because of the difference\Nin size, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.12,0:14:03.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I got her face!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.46,0:14:20.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One more time, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:34.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:34.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson One is cleared!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:40.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why? I lost to her, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:46.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I didn't say a thing about\Ndowning Ururu to clear Lesson One.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:52.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she has the fighting skills\Nto counter Soul Reapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:56.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No way can a human soul beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:15:00.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, are you still\Nhaving trouble breathing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:02.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:06.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which means, the restoration\Nof your spiritual energy was successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This lesson was for one-shot battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:12.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you could dodge\Nthe first attack or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:18.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Spiritual energy increases fastest when\Nthe soul is in danger of being destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.88,0:15:20.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you can raise your spiritual\Nenergy sufficiently,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then you can dodge the punch\Nand it’s all good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And if I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.50,0:15:27.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say so first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:33.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I had faith in you...\Nthat you would succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.55,0:15:38.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, your spiritual energy\Nis back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:40.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So...let's celebrate and...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.31,0:15:49.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go straight into Lesson Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.39,0:15:51.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:53.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you interested in taking it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:56.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, so out of the blue like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:16:00.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, the problem is...\NThe cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.44,0:16:02.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.97,0:16:03.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.31,0:16:09.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo has begun preparations\Nto enter the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:15.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you also want to use the powers\Nthat have awakened inside you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:17.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,then take my lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:21.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You can decide whether\Nyou're really going or not after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:25.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.48,0:16:26.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.26,0:16:34.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:50.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! There! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.02,0:16:53.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu! Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.72,0:16:56.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Orihime! Chad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:59.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:02.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We asked Yoruichi to follow\Nyour spiritual aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:03.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.38,0:17:08.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're training, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.32,0:17:12.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:16.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you looking?\NOver here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:19.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:22.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! A cat?! A cat is--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So? What's the big deal just\Nbecause a cat can talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:26.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be such a wimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:29.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Uryu. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:35.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't think it's strange if\None is mildly traumatized by it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:40.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Men have such\Na hard time adapting to things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.82,0:17:44.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. But what did\Nyou want with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo is going to the Soul Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo is going to rescue Rukia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.98,0:17:57.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought we should tell you, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it's got nothing\Nto do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.98,0:18:03.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia's life is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.92,0:18:08.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Quincy and I can't forgive myself\Nfor losing to a Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.20,0:18:09.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I train.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia is not my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.55,0:18:24.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You're doing your best\Nin your own way, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:30.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think it over carefully again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:34.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's certain that\NI'm undergoing changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid, but I want to\Nknow what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Uryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.93,0:18:55.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry Orihime...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.94,0:19:01.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let anyone\Nsee this training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.88,0:19:09.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch over me, Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.57,0:19:18.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:21.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely. Once the Chain of Fate\Nis broken,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:24.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you can no longer return\Nto your physical body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.82,0:19:26.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’ll just die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:28.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit talking like it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:30.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let me tell you\Nsomething that does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:33.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The chain will begin the Encroachment\Nat the point of severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.79,0:19:35.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And when it reaches your chest,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.66,0:19:38.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you will become a Hollow...\Nand it will be the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.35,0:19:39.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to become a Hollow,\Nyou must become a Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:46.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once you clear Lesson Two,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.25,0:19:52.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you will regain the powers of\Na Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.92,0:19:55.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which you choose is your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.17,0:19:59.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! You don’t have to ask me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.88,0:20:02.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Then let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.88,0:20:04.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you shocked?\NBy my ruse?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.32,0:20:15.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.38,0:20:17.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's awfully deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:18.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.88,0:20:27.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.51,0:20:32.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--!\NWhat are these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.53,0:20:34.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Binding Spell 99 –
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:35.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Restrict!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was bold of me,\Nbut until this lesson is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:42.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,your arms shall be sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Why you--!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:47.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.34,0:20:51.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Climb back up here\Nin that condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:56.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is the lesson...\Notherwise called Shattered Shaft.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! As if I can do such a thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.93,0:21:02.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you have time to\Nwonder whether you can or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:19.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At the bottom of the Shattered Shaft,\Nyou have 72 hours, or three days,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.18,0:21:22.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,before the chain is\Ncompletely Encroached.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.23,0:21:26.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must come back up here\Nas a Soul Reaper before the time is up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:31.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise,\Nwe'll have to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:46.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.80,0:21:49.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:52.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.57,0:21:58.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.40,0:22:00.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:05.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.93,0:22:08.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:10.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:12.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.40,0:22:14.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:16.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:18.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.76,0:22:21.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.00,0:22:23.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.28,0:22:26.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:28.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:30.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.80,0:22:32.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.59,0:22:35.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.12,0:22:37.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jinta! Ururu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:41.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How quickly do you think Ichigo\Ncan come back as a Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:43.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I say five hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.16,0:22:44.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,About 12 hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.60,0:22:47.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll wager a thousand points\Non him not returning...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:48.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, you!